- Add github deploy key.
  [msom]

0.0.2 (2017-07-17)
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

- Sends emails on publish/reject.
  [msom]

- Adds a copy option.
  [msom]

- Adds statistics views.
  [msom]

- Adds a preview view.
  [msom]

0.0.1 (unreleased)
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

- Initial Release.
  [msom]


